# ============================================================
# RELATIONSHIP DETAIL OPERATIONS
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: operations
domain: detail
subdomain: relationship-detail
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

purpose:
Defines operational handling for relationship detail.

scope:
Covers relation-detail publication, trust-scope review,
historical relation inspection, and containment of unsafe relation exposure.

required_behavior:
- Support relation-detail publication.
- Support trust-detail masking review.
- Support historical relation inspection.
- Support broken-relation archival handling.
- Support containment for unsafe internal trust exposure.

state_model:
relationship_detail_operational_state:
- prepared
- reviewed
- active
- suspended
- broken
- archived
- contained

validation_rules:
- subject_ref and object_ref are required.
- relation_type and direction are required.
- broken relations must not remain active.
- internal trust nuance must not be published into public-safe mode.

transition_rules:
- prepared -> reviewed
- reviewed -> active
- active -> suspended
- suspended -> active
- active -> broken
- broken -> archived
- active -> contained
- contained -> suspended

operational_focus:
- trust-scope review
- broken-relation archival handling
- public versus internal relation audit
- historical relation inspection

failure_codes:
- RELATIONSHIP_DETAIL_OP_SUBJECT_MISSING
- RELATIONSHIP_DETAIL_OP_OBJECT_MISSING
- RELATIONSHIP_DETAIL_OP_TYPE_INVALID
- RELATIONSHIP_DETAIL_OP_PUBLIC_TRUST_LEAK
